title: Food Jammers
overview: Ever balked at the boundaries of your own kitchen? Wondered what it would be like to enjoy gastronomic delights straight from the fruitful loins of your garage, art studio, automobile, or even the great outdoors? Canadian food lovers Micah, Chris, and Nobu--along with their beloved dog Brooklyn--are ready and willing to show you the way. From kick-the-can ice cream to hot tub hot pots, the culinary creations of Food Jammers are the stuff of Emeril's nightmares and your own very sweet dreams. The icing on this already delectable cake? A rock-and-roll soundtrack featuring some of the best bands you've never heard.
